God's highlights and my story. Do I have any complaints from life? NO.  Because if life had not been so rich with experiences, I would never have been a learner. Embrace each and every ups and downs of life. That will shape you. Be a learner in the school of life. Remember life is too short. Enjoy and savour each and every moment. Spread positive vibes and never let anyone dim your light. Your soul is on it's journey. Life is just an experience.

…trend to get to know each other…
5 facts about me
1. I am an introvert. I take my time to open up.
2. I couldn’t pursue college after my grade 12 and resumed my studies after 5 years of break.
3. I speak Punjabi but I can’t read the language. (Learning now)
4. I have never coloured my hair, they are virgin grey.
5. When I started to grey, first thing I wanted to do was pierce my nose, and after trying for 4 times, I finally got it right!

Tell me something about you.

Life these days 😅
